394
00:19:10,816 --> 00:19:12,901
[Celestino] <i>Did you move the body?</i>

395
00:19:12,985 --> 00:19:15,571
[sobbing] <i>We wanted</i>
<i>to take her to the hospital.</i>

396
00:19:15,654 --> 00:19:17,573
<i>- Get out of the way!</i>
- [crowd chattering]

397
00:19:17,656 --> 00:19:20,576
<i>- Mel? Are you okay?</i>
<i>- Daddy!</i> [sobbing]

398
00:19:22,369 --> 00:19:24,246
<i>Did you even check her condition first?</i>

399
00:19:24,329 --> 00:19:26,039
<i>Or did you go</i>
<i>straight to asking questions?</i>

400
00:19:26,123 --> 00:19:27,916
<i>We checked all of them.</i>

401
00:19:28,458 --> 00:19:30,627
<i>No one was hurt except the victim.</i>

402
00:19:31,712 --> 00:19:33,505
<i>A guy wearing a black hoodie jacket.</i>

403
00:19:33,881 --> 00:19:35,382
<i>And he was wearing a cap?</i>

404
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:39,720
<i>Are you actually looking for him?</i>
<i>What if he gets away?</i>

405
00:19:39,803 --> 00:19:43,557
<i>I hope he doesn't attack another person.</i>

406
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:46,018
<i>Any idea who did this to the victim?</i>

407
00:19:46,101 --> 00:19:48,353
<i>Can we do this some other time?</i>

408
00:19:48,437 --> 00:19:51,481
<i>My daughter is in no</i>
<i>condition to answer your questions.</i>

409
00:19:52,316 --> 00:19:56,987
<i>Have you seen</i>
<i>anything missing from the victim?</i>

410
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:59,323
<i>- Aside from her cellphone.</i>
- [young Erica sobbing]

411
00:20:01,658 --> 00:20:04,620
<i>Oh my gosh! Someone gave you that watch!</i>

412
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:08,457
<i>I knew it! That's why</i>
<i>you won't tell us where you got it.</i>

413
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,375
