<i>- You have a boyfriend?</i>

414
00:20:13,712 --> 00:20:16,465
<i>- Secret!</i>
<i>- Let me see!</i>

415
00:20:16,548 --> 00:20:18,926
<i>- No! You might break it!</i>
- [young Beth] <i>Hold her!</i>

416
00:20:19,009 --> 00:20:21,011
<i>Stop resisting. You'll hurt yourself.</i>

417
00:20:21,094 --> 00:20:22,638
<i>- Aha!</i>
<i>- Wait!</i>

418
00:20:22,721 --> 00:20:25,057
- [young Beth] <i>Bleh! Bleh!</i>
- [young Alice] <i>Let me see!</i>

419
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:27,142
<i>- Oh! Something's written on it.</i>
- [Young Mel] <i>What is it?</i>

420
00:20:27,226 --> 00:20:32,481
<i>It's the letter L.</i>
<i>Is it L for Louisa or L for lover?</i>

421
00:20:33,315 --> 00:20:35,984
<i>- You're keeping secrets now!</i>
<i>- Hey! Hey!</i>

422
00:20:36,443 --> 00:20:38,654
<i>Hang in there, Louisa!</i>

423
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:43,408
<i>She's not wearing her watch.</i>

424
00:20:44,117 --> 00:20:47,287
<i>She always wears</i>
<i>it with our friendship bracelet.</i>

425
00:20:48,038 --> 00:20:50,249
<i>You didn't recognize the suspect?</i>

426
00:20:50,332 --> 00:20:53,961
<i>Excuse me, sir. Erica, Beth!</i>

427
00:20:54,044 --> 00:20:55,671
<i>Beth, where's my sister? Louisa?</i>

428
00:20:56,421 --> 00:20:58,423
- [Celestino] <i>Hey! Wait!</i>
- [man] <i>Louisa!</i>

429
00:20:58,507 --> 00:21:00,634
